items.title: Awesome Jax
items.content_text: ### Libraries / New Libraries * [JAX Toolbox (‚≠ê321)](https://github.com/NVIDIA/JAX-Toolbox) - Nightly CI and optimized examples for JAX on NVIDIA GPUs using libraries such as T5x, Paxml, and Transformer Engine. ### Tutorials and Blog Posts / NumPyro * [Learn JAX: From Linear Regression to Neural Networks by Rito Ghosh](https://www.kaggle.com/code/truthr/jax-0) - A gentle introduction to JAX and using it to implement Linear and Logistic Regression, and Neural Network models and using them to solve real world problems.

items.title: Awesome Security
items.content_text:
### Web / Scanning / Pentesting

*   [CakeFuzzer (‚≠ê99)](https://github.com/Zigrin-Security/CakeFuzzer) - The ultimate web application security testing tool for CakePHP-based web applications. CakeFuzzer employs a predefined set of attacks that are randomly modified before execution. Leveraging its deep understanding of the Cake PHP framework, Cake Fuzzer launches attacks on all potential application entry points.
items.content_html:
